{"tid":1203742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊製作手提lock screen wallpaper以備於搜身及被捕後使用","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T16:01:33.000Z","uid":185935,"like":486,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d5715ba621ab4b9eb7b8ba822d68cdfe5317c8d7","tid":1203742,"uid":185935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"如果不幸被捕又唔想喺人面前unlock電話，就可以用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdKABS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdKABS8.jpg&h=a0148062&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果畀警察逗完佢仲想無理搜身，即時show返畀佢地睇：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coZH1jO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoZH1jO.jpg&h=888769fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個反白版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Gmn1jP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Gmn1jP.jpg&h=70fd6210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年時，啲差佬屈會屈人偷電話，要用unlock証明<br />\n而當時我地有人換晒自己個樣做wallpaper，<br />\n當然，叫佢打一次個電話都得，但唔知會預到咩情況<br />\n亦唔知呢招宜家仲有冇用，但都希望大家可以參考<br />\n<br />\n大家諗到咩都可以幫手整，其實打定字printscreen就得"},{"pid":"e5787e414f5a1705caf0503dabb118f03c751be9","tid":1203742,"uid":185070,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86559a5ce83429f608db2a972062940f5f7c690e","tid":1203742,"uid":144056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abd52b5bf66ad4b7aae30a76837d63a0431c6f0f","tid":1203742,"uid":196252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9a9877bce372e2cf24db6b061ffff06e181ecf3","tid":1203742,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1fc42334905e0e8007dd5409898762d7333068ee","tid":1203742,"uid":85450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:21:46.000Z",