br />\n其他版本嘅設定方法應該大同小異，有錯請指正。"},{"pid":"6469a2febe97c3312f84dfdb52419f47f91dbd72","tid":1203742,"uid":104793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱整咗medical id 好方便<br />\n唔駛unlock都show 到名+出生日期<br />\n唔輪到佢屈我偷電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfc5979fb2a87fd3de7b54ad35d7994cbe015cb","tid":1203742,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3103c8a1e01ac0231c63559d0ca03408a1070032","tid":1203742,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48102a49f14905da07264af3a06fefcbc9343694","tid":1203742,"uid":144056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f6341dbc817a44b2eb6ba46fb5bc1f68f5b142c","tid":1203742,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53445e181daafe783a8bc5753eb57da5dbd82df","tid":1203742,"uid":190164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"好有用"},{"pid":"8392a6d4545a607caa8c260ff2dd0f5834edaa7a","tid":1203742,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}